+# 13.15.35
+
+### Fixes, New Locales and Enhancements
+
+- [#2663](https://github.com/validatorjs/validator.js/pull/2663) `isISO31661Alpha2`/`isISO31661Alpha3`: add support for Kosovo (`XK` / `XXK`) @johanpoirier-d4
